  "text": "The goal of designing randomized servers algorithms on HSTs has been previously approached by Seiden [CITATION_1] . He showed that for a µ-HST with µ ≈ k, low height and small degree, there is polylog(k) competitive algorithm. Unfortunately, this result is not applicable to the general problem because of the condition on µ.",
